{
  "name": "DataBarBorder",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>DataBarBorder</strong> 对象可获取或设置数据条的颜色和边框类型。若要访问与数据条条件格式规则关联的 <strong>DataBarBorder</strong> 对象，请使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Databar/Databar .htm#Databar.BarBorder\">BarBorder</a></strong> 属性。在检索 <strong>DataBarBorder</strong> 对象后，使用其 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/DataBarBorder/DataBarBorder .htm#DataBarBorder.Color\">Color</a></strong> 属性返回可用来设置数据条颜色的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选择一个单元格区域，将数据条条件格式规则添加到该区域，使用BarBorder属性检索与该规则关联的DataBarBorder对象，然后设置数据条的颜色、淡色和类型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddDatabar</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBarBorder = dataBar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BarBorder</span>\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlDataBarBorderSolid\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent2\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的边框为实心边框，则设置该边框的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBarBorder = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">BarBorder</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlDataBarBorderSolid) {\n        dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示由条件格式规则指定的数据条的边框。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个指定数据条（由条件格式规则指定的数据条）边框色的对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选择一个单元格区域，将数据条条件格式规则添加到该区域，使用BarBorder属性检索与该规则关联的DataBarBorder对象，然后设置数据条的颜色、淡色和类型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddDatabar</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBarBorder = dataBar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BarBorder</span>\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlDataBarBorderSolid\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent2\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的边框的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBarBorder = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">BarBorder</span>\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置由条件格式规则指定的数据条的边框类型。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选择一个单元格区域，将数据条条件格式规则添加到该区域，使用BarBorder属性检索与该规则关联的DataBarBorder对象，然后设置数据条的颜色、淡色和类型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddDatabar</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBarBorder = dataBar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BarBorder</span>\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlDataBarBorderSolid\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent2\n    dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的边框的类型是否为xlDataBarBorderSolid。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBarBorder = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">BarBorder</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(dataBarBorder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlDataBarBorderSolid)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlDataBarBorderType 枚举.html\">XlDataBarBorderType</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}